highlights.text: Bente has the most spots on Viral Songs Netherlands. “Kan Je Me Zien” is the highest at #2.
“Baila de Gasolina” by Effe Serieus has been on Viral Songs Netherlands the longest, at 200 days straight.
“Here With Me” by d4vd is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Netherlands, up 20 spots at #62.
“Instant Moments” by Divasi is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Netherlands at #22.
